msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/mission_option_select1"
msgid "Select your Doctrine for the mission:"
msgstr "Seleccione su Estrategia para la misión:"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/fail_bridge"
msgid ""
"German armour crossed the bridge. You had strict orders to prevent that."
msgstr ""
"Los blindados alemanes cruzaron el puente. Tenías órdenes estrictas de "
"impedirlo."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/fail_stretchers"
msgid "You lost too many stretchers with wounded soldiers!"
msgstr "¡Has perdido demasiadas camillas con soldados heridos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/name"
msgid "Christmas Trouble"
msgstr "Problemas navideños"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/name_big"
msgid "Christmas Trouble"
msgstr "Problemas navideños"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/01"
msgid ""
"Christ! The weather is god damn attrocious! It seems we're getting screwed "
"both in combat and when we're in reserve..."
msgstr ""
"¡Dios! ¡El tiempo es jodidamente atroz! Parece que estamos jodidos tanto en "
"combate como descansando..."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/02"
msgid "Calm down Soldier. The Krauts here? How is that even possible?"
msgstr "Cálmate, soldado. ¿Los alemanes aquí? ¿Cómo es eso posible?"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/03"
msgid "Get ready, everyone! Take your positions and hold this checkpoint!"
msgstr "¡Preparaos, todos! ¡Tomad posiciones y defended este punto de control!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/04"
msgid ""
"Enemy tanks! God damn it! We only have bazookas to deal with them, make the "
"best of it!"
msgstr ""
"¡Tanques enemigos! ¡Maldita sea! Sólo tenemos bazookas para enfrentarnos a "
"ellos, ¡hacedlo lo mejor que podáis!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/05"
msgid "Panthers! Bloody Panthers! "
msgstr "¡Panthers! ¡Malditos Panthers! "

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/06"
msgid "You there! What the hell are you doing?"
msgstr "¡Tú! ¿Qué demonios estás haciendo?"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/07"
msgid ""
"Your tank's broke. Why on earth don't you fix it? We could definitely use "
"it, you know?"
msgstr ""
"Tu tanque está roto. ¿Por qué diablos no lo arreglas? Podríamos usarlo, "
"¿sabes?"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/08"
msgid "Useless bunch of drunks! My men will take care of it."
msgstr "¡Vaya montón de borrachos inútiles! Mis hombres se encargarán de ello."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/09"
msgid ""
"We are unable to hold the Germans in the open! Fall back to HQ! We'll get "
"those Panthers with bazookas in close quarters combat."
msgstr ""
"¡No podemos contener a los alemanes en campo abierto! ¡Retírense al cuartel "
"general! Derribaremos a esos Panthers con bazookas en combate cuerpo a "
"cuerpo."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/10"
msgid ""
"We also need to evacuate our wounded. I order you to transport the "
"stretchers to the other side of the river, where the Germans will be kept at "
"bay."
msgstr ""
"También necesitamos evacuar a nuestros heridos. Te ordeno que transportes "
"las camillas al otro lado del río, donde mantendremos a los alemanes a raya."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/11"
msgid ""
"We've managed to keep the Germans back but they've overrun the town and we "
"cannot match their numbers. Our only chance is to fall back and concentrate "
"all our forces in defending the bridge. Get it done, Soldiers!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos conseguido contener a los alemanes, pero han invadido la ciudad y no "
"podemos igualar su número. Nuestra única oportunidad es retroceder y "
"concentrar todas nuestras fuerzas en defender el puente. ¡Háganlo, soldados!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/12"
msgid ""
"We have a Slugger ready to shred through some Kraut armor. Give them hell, "
"Soldiers! Show them how our 90's roll."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos un Slugger listo para destrozar algo de blindaje alemán. ¡Llevadlos "
"al infierno, soldados! Mostradles cómo ruedan nuestros 90."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/13"
msgid ""
"The Krauts understand that they are sitting ducks against our bazookas and "
"grenades the moment they stand still. They plan to overwhelm us and break "
"right through our lines without stopping. Do not let that happen. Not a "
"SINGLE german tank is to cross this bridge. Understood?"
msgstr ""
"Los alemanes entienden que son blancos fáciles contra nuestras bazucas y "
"granadas en cuanto se quedan quietos. Planean abrumarnos y atravesar "
"nuestras líneas sin detenerse. No dejen que eso suceda. Ni un solo tanque "
"alemán debe cruzar este puente. ¿Entendido?"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/14"
msgid ""
"Well done Soldiers. The Germans are now on the defensive. That will show "
"them!"
msgstr ""
"Bien hecho soldados. Los alemanes están ahora a la defensiva. ¡Eso les "
"enseñará!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/15"
msgid ""
"Alright Gentlemen. We managed to mobilise our reserves. With these "
"reinforcements, I order you to take back Hotton from the Germans. The "
"documents and supplies in our HQ are too valuable to let the Krauts have em."
msgstr ""
"Muy bien, caballeros. Logramos movilizar nuestras reservas. Con los "
"refuerzos actuales, les ordeno recuperar Hotton de manos de los alemanes. "
"Los documentos y suministros de nuestro cuartel general son demasiado "
"valiosos para dejar que los alemanes los tengan."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/16"
msgid ""
"The Boches brought in heavy artillery! That's gonna throw in a wrench in our "
"plans! Make sure to advance during the reloads between salvos."
msgstr ""
"¡Los Boches trajeron artillería pesada! ¡Eso va a estropear nuestros planes! "
"Asegúrate de avanzar durante las recargas entre salvas."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator/scout/01"
msgid "Germans! Germans! The damn Krauts are coming in half-tracks and armor!"
msgstr ""
"¡Alemanes! ¡Alemanes! ¡Los malditos alemanes vienen en semiorugas y "
"blindados!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator2/01"
msgid "We're eating cheese and drinking beer."
msgstr "Estamos comiendo queso y bebiendo cerveza."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/narrator2/02"
msgid "Oh, man. We only ride'em, we don't know what makes 'em work..."
msgstr "Oh, tío. Nosotros sólo los conducimos, no sabemos cómo funcionan..."

#, boost-format
msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/obj3_progress"
msgid ""
"%1% out of at least 10 stretchers evacuated to the other side of the river."
msgstr "%1% de al menos 10 camillas evacuadas al otro lado del río."

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Excellent work soldier! This victory is evidence of your bravery and "
"tenacity in the face of overwhelming odds. You certainly made a favorable "
"impression on your superiors today. We will report this victory to General "
"Rose’s HQ immediately. Well done!"
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente trabajo, soldado! Esta victoria es una prueba de su valentía y "
"tenacidad frente a un peligro abrumador. Sin duda hoy ha causado una "
"impresión favorable a sus superiores. Informaremos de esta victoria al "
"Cuartel del General Rose inmediatamente. ¡Bravo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"This is not going to go down well with General Rose. There is only one thing "
"you can do, and that is to try again and try something different this time. "
"We can’t allow this to happen!"
msgstr ""
"Esto no le va a gustar al General Rose. Sólo hay una cosa que puedes hacer, "
"y es intentarlo de nuevo con algo diferente esta vez. ¡No podemos permitir "
"que esto suceda!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/place"
msgid "3rd Armored Division 'Spearhead'"
msgstr "3ª División Blindada \"Spearhead\""

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/story"
msgid " December 1944. After 6 months of advancing since D-Day, you and everybody else got a big surprise a couple of days ago. In appalling winter weather, the Germans have launched a massive counteroffensive in the Ardennes region! They are pushing into Belgium, with orders to take Antwerp. Our commanders have sent out task forces on a number of roads that lead to the southwest to recon and intercept the German Kampfgruppen. We have no information on the whereabouts of the task forces, or those of the Germans.\n\n In this mission, you will be in charge of the main road checkpoint, close to our forward HQ. Our HQ and our field hospital have been set up in the town. Set up a defense perimeter around the roadblocks to deny access to the town. Get your men to dig in and await further orders.\n\nGood luck!"
msgstr ""
"Diciembre de 1944.\n"
"\n"
"Después de 6 meses de avance desde el Día-D,\n"
"\n"
"tu y todos los demás recibisteis una gran sorpresa hace un par de días.\n"
"\n"
"¡Con un clima invernal espantoso, los alemanes han lanzado\n"
"\n"
"una contraofensiva masiva en la región de las Ardenas!\n"
"\n"
"Están avanzando hacia Bélgica, con órdenes de\n"
"\n"
"tomar Amberes. Nuestros comandantes han enviado fuerzas de tarea\n"
"\n"
"a una serie de carreteras que conducen al suroeste\n"
"\n"
"para reconocer e interceptar los Kampfgruppen alemanes.\n"
"\n"
"No tenemos información sobre el paradero de las\n"
"\n"
"fuerzas de tarea, o los de los alemanes.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"En esta misión, usted estará a cargo del principal\n"
"\n"
"puesto de control de carretera, cerca de nuestro cuartel general.\n"
"\n"
"Nuestro cuartel general y nuestro hospital de campaña se han instalado en la "
"ciudad.\n"
"\n"
"Establezcan un perímetro defensivo alrededor de\n"
"\n"
"los bloqueos para impedir el acceso a la ciudad.\n"
"\n"
"Haz que tus hombres se atrincheren y esperen nuevas órdenes.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"¡Buena suerte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/task1"
msgid "Defend the Checkpoint"
msgstr "Defender el puesto de control"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/task2"
msgid "Defend the Checkpoint"
msgstr "Defender el puesto de control"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/task3"
msgid "Defend the HQ"
msgstr "Defender el cuartel general"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/task4"
msgid "Evacuate the wounded from the field hospital"
msgstr "Evacuar a los heridos del hospital de campaña"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/task5"
msgid "Defend the bridge and don't let the germans through"
msgstr "Defiende el puente y no dejes pasar a los alemanes"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/task6"
msgid "Retake the town"
msgstr "Retomar la ciudad"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/task_sec1"
msgid "Secret objective"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/task_sec1c"
msgid "Secret Objective: Repair the stranded tank!"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto: ¡Repara el tanque varado!"

msgctxt "mission/single/04-usa/1944_12_hotton/timer"
msgid "Defend the HQ for:"
msgstr "Defiende el cuartel general de:"
